HEADWORD: Mantling
<hw>Man"tling</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Her.)</fld>
<def>The representation of a mantle, or the drapery behind and around a
coat of arms: -- called also <altname>lambrequin</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

